        "readme": {
          "childMarkdownRemark": {
            "html": "<h1 align=\"center\" style=\"border-bottom: none;\">gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources</h1>\n<h2 align=\"center\">Provides drop-in support for Stylus with or without CSS Modules, with shared resources (e.g. variables, mixins etc.)</h2>\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://travis-ci.com/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\">\n        <img alt=\"travis build\" src=\"https://travis-ci.com/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources.svg?branch=master\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\">\n        <img alt=\"npm version\" src=\"https://badgen.net/npm/v/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"#badge\">\n        <img alt=\"dependencies status\" src=\"https://badgen.net/david/dep/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"#badge\">\n        <img alt=\"dev dependencies status\" src=\"https://badgen.net/david/dev/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"http://commitizen.github.io/cz-cli/\">\n        <img alt=\"commitizen\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/commitizen-friendly-brightgreen.svg\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release\">\n        <img alt=\"semantic-release\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/%20%20%F0%9F%93%A6%F0%9F%9A%80-semantic--release-e10079.svg\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/prettier\">\n        <img alt=\"prettier\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/styled_with-prettier-ff69b4.svg\">\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources/blob/master/LICENSE\">\n        <img alt=\"license\" src=\"https://badgen.net/github/license/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n<p>This is an extended version of <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/tree/master/packages/gatsby-plugin-stylus\">gatsby-plugin-stylus</a>.</p>\n<p>The only difference is the use of <a href=\"https://github.com/shakacode/sass-resources-loader\">sass-resources-loader</a> so you can use your shared variables &#x26; mixins across all <code class=\"language-text\">.styl</code> files without manually importing them in each file.</p>\n<p><strong>Feel free to check out and run the <a href=\"https://github.com/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources/tree/master/example\">example folder</a> for detailed configuration.</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm i gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources -d</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources -D</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-label=\"usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create your file (or files) with resources :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"styl\"><pre class=\"language-styl\"><code class=\"language-styl\">/* styles/config/mixins.styl */\n\nflexbox($value = row)\n    display: flex\n    flex-direction: $value\n\ntruncate($fontsize = 14px)\n    flexbox()\n    height: $fontsize + 4px\n    white-space: nowrap\n    overflow: hidden\n    text-overflow: ellipsis</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Include the plugin in your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> file :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* gatsby-config.js */</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        resources<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'./src/styles/config/mixins.styl'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'path/to/another/file.styl'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>⚠️ <strong>Do not include anything that will be actually rendered in CSS</strong>, because it will be added to every imported <code class=\"language-text\">.styl</code> file.</p>\n<h3 id=\"without-css-modules\"><a href=\"#without-css-modules\" aria-label=\"without css modules permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Without CSS Modules</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"with-css-modules\"><a href=\"#with-css-modules\" aria-label=\"with css modules permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>With CSS Modules</h3>\n<p>Using CSS modules requires no additional configuration. Simply prepend <code class=\"language-text\">.module</code> to the extension. For example: <code class=\"language-text\">App.styl</code> -> <code class=\"language-text\">App.module.styl</code>.\nAny file with the <code class=\"language-text\">module</code> extension will use CSS modules.</p>\n<h3 id=\"with-stylus-plugins\"><a href=\"#with-stylus-plugins\" aria-label=\"with stylus plugins permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>With Stylus plugins</h3>\n<p>This plugin has the same API as\n<a href=\"https://github.com/shama/stylus-loader#stylus-plugins\">stylus-loader</a>, which\nmeans you can add stylus plugins with <code class=\"language-text\">use</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> rupture <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"rupture\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        use<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token function\">rupture</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"postcss-plugins\"><a href=\"#postcss-plugins\" aria-label=\"postcss plugins permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PostCSS plugins</h3>\n<p>PostCSS is also included to handle some default optimizations like autoprefixing a\nand common cross-browser flexbox bugs. Normally you don’t need to think about it, but if\nyou’d prefer to add additional postprocessing to your Stylus output you can sepecify plugins\nin the plugin options</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-stylus-resources</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      postCssPlugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token function\">somePostCssPlugin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"contributing\"><a href=\"#contributing\" aria-label=\"contributing permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contributing</h2>\n<p>Contributions are welcome ! See <a href=\"https://github.com/JimmyBeldone/gatsby-plugin-webpack-bundle-analyser-v2/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">contributing guidelines</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"license\"><a href=\"#license\" aria-label=\"license permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>License</h2>\n<p>MIT</p>\n<p>Copyright (c) 2019 Jimmy Beldone</p>",
